Class DataEvent

java.lang.Object
  |

        +--com.esri.mo2.data.feat.DataEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class DataEvent
extends EventObject

A MapDataset object sends this event to a DataListener when an error is detected during a MapDataset.search().

The error is an Exception subclass.

See Also:
DataListener, Serialized Form
